<p style=3D"text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: center;">Sub:&nbsp; Prohibition of use / possession=
 of mobile phone during Quizess/End Semester Exam =96 reg.
</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: center;">***</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: justify;">All students / scholars are hereby inform=
ed that the possession / use of mobile phone or other communication devices=
 in the Examination Hall is prohibited.</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: justify;">Students / scholars should leave their mo=
bile phones in their bag.</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: justify;">Use of IPAD / LAPTOP etc. are not allowed=
 unless specifically permitted by concerned faculty.</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: justify;">Any violation brought to the attention by=
 the invigilator will be reported to the Disciplinary and Welfare Committee=
.
